This is how to same_chars of s0 and s1:
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this s0's length times:
      Remember that c is item i in s0
      When c is not in s1, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   Remember that j is 0
   Do this s1's length times:
      Remember that c is item j in s1
      When c is not in s0, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      Increase j
   End do

   The answer is 1
